pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: logo
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 28, 120, 24]
    content:
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:14px; color:$primary; letter-spacing:3px;"><strong>BRINC</strong></span></p>
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      align: [left, middle]
  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1180, 28, 40, 24]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      text: |
        <p>06</p>
      wrap: false
      align: [right, middle]
  - elementId: title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 70, 800, 45]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      fontSize: 32
      text: |
        <p><strong>Hi2 Tech Incubator — Dubai DET</strong></p>
      wrap: false
      align: [left, middle]
  - elementId: accent-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 120, 60, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: sector-badge
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 145, 120, 28]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: sector-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 145, 120, 28]
    content:
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:12px; color:#FFFFFF;"><strong>Government / Tech</strong></span></p>
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      align: [center, middle]
  - elementId: background-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 200, 200, 28]
    content:
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:14px; color:$primary; letter-spacing:2px;"><strong>BACKGROUND</strong></span></p>
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      align: [left, middle]
  - elementId: background-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 235, 540, 120]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      text: |
        <p>DET engaged Brinc to design and deliver a 16-week incubator for 20 Emirati founders, aligned with Dubai's D33 economic agenda. The program needed to cover ideation through MVP validation with structured mentorship.</p>
      align: [left, top]
  - elementId: details-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 375, 200, 28]
    content:
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:14px; color:$primary; letter-spacing:2px;"><strong>WHAT WE DID</strong></span></p>
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      align: [left, middle]
  - elementId: details-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 410, 540, 140]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      text: |
        <ul>
        <li>Designed complete program framework with 16-week curriculum</li>
        <li>Sourced and selected 20 Emirati founders across 7 D33 priority sectors</li>
        <li>Delivered hybrid format with weekly workshops and 1:1 mentorship</li>
        </ul>
      align: [left, top]
  - elementId: outcome-box
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 200, 580, 360]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightgray"
  - elementId: outcome-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [665, 220, 530, 28]
    content:
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:14px; color:$primary; letter-spacing:2px;"><strong>OUTCOME</strong></span></p>
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      align: [left, middle]
  - elementId: outcome-stat1
    elementType: text
    bounds: [665, 265, 250, 50]
    content:
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:36px; color:$accent;"><strong>20</strong></span></p>
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      align: [left, bottom]
  - elementId: outcome-stat1-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [665, 318, 250, 25]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      text: |
        <p>Founders graduated</p>
      wrap: false
      align: [left, middle]
  - elementId: outcome-stat2
    elementType: text
    bounds: [930, 265, 250, 50]
    content:
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:36px; color:$accent;"><strong>7</strong></span></p>
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      align: [left, bottom]
  - elementId: outcome-stat2-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [930, 318, 250, 25]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      text: |
        <p>Priority sectors covered</p>
      wrap: false
      align: [left, middle]
  - elementId: outcome-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [665, 365, 530, 170]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      text: |
        <p>Program currently ongoing with strong engagement. Founders have completed Business Model Canvas, conducted 100+ customer interviews, and built initial MVPs. Demo Day scheduled for GITEX 2026.</p>
      align: [left, top]